        <address>
          <ul class="contact-list">
            <li><span>Location:</span> <span>Saint Petersburg, Russia</span></li>
            <li><span>Telegram:</span> <a href="https://t.me/yaleksandr89" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow">https://t.me/yaleksandr89</a></li>
            <li><span>Email:</span> <a href="mailto:y.aleksandr89@gmail.com">y.aleksandr89@gmail.com</a></li>
            <li><span>LinkedIn:</span> <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/yaleksandr89" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow">https://linkedin.com/in/yaleksandr89</a></li>
