      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="sidebar-section">
      <h2>Courses</h2>
      <div class="sidebar-section__body">
        <p>Section content will be added in the next step.</p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>

  <section class="content-section">
    <h2>Professional Summary</h2>
    <div class="content-section__body">
      <p>PHP Backend Developer with over 5 years of commercial experience in web application development and maintenance.</p>
      <p>Worked on a B2B travel booking system, corporate portals, internal accounting systems, and public sector projects. Main focus areas include backend development with PHP, Laravel and Symfony, third-party integrations, API development, and legacy project improvement.</p>
      <p>Focused on product-oriented development, service stability, and improving backend architecture.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="content-section">
    <h2>Work Experience</h2>
    <div class="content-section__body">
      <article class="experience-entry">
        <header class="experience-entry__header">
          <h3>PHP Developer</h3>
          <p class="experience-entry__meta">
            <span>Russian Express — tour operator</span>
            <a href="https://r-express.ru" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow">r-express.ru</a>
          </p>
          <p class="experience-entry__period">November 2024 — March 2026</p>
        </header>
        <p>Contributed to the development and maintenance of a B2B travel booking system for agencies and partners. Worked as part of a cross-functional product team including backend developers, an analyst, and a project manager.</p>
        <div class="experience-entry__technologies">
          <p class="experience-entry__label">Technologies:</p>
          <ul class="technology-list">
            <li>PHP 8</li>
            <li>Laravel</li>
            <li>MariaDB</li>
            <li>Redis</li>
            <li>Docker</li>
            <li>Elasticsearch</li>
            <li>GitLab</li>
            <li>Ubuntu</li>
            <li>PhpStorm</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <p><strong>Responsibilities and achievements:</strong></p>
        <ul class="experience-entry__list">
          <li>Contributed to expanding the booking system functionality for new sales markets and B2B partners.</li>
          <li>Improved integrations with ERP/1C and internal services.</li>
          <li>Refactored part of the API interactions from a polling model to a push model to reduce the number of requests to the 1C server.</li>
          <li>Extended the refund and payment transfer mechanism between orders.</li>
          <li>Optimized Elasticsearch usage: improved search logic and contributed to splitting a shared index with 15+ million documents into separate indexes by section.</li>
          <li>Participated in the gradual separation of a monolithic legacy application into internal and external packages.</li>
        </ul>
      </article>

      <hr class="experience-divider" />

      <article class="experience-entry">
        <header class="experience-entry__header">
          <h3>Software Developer</h3>
          <p class="experience-entry__meta">
            <span>WONE IT — development and maintenance of corporate solutions</span>
            <a href="https://wone-it.ru" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow">wone-it.ru</a>
          </p>
          <p class="experience-entry__period">July 2023 — August 2024</p>
