        <div class="experience-entry__technologies">
          <p class="experience-entry__label">Technologies:</p>
          <ul class="technology-list">
            <li>PHP 8</li>
            <li>MariaDB</li>
            <li>PostgreSQL</li>
            <li>Git</li>
            <li>GitLab</li>
            <li>Gitea</li>
            <li>JavaScript</li>
            <li>Zabbix</li>
            <li>Ubuntu</li>
            <li>PhpStorm</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <p><strong>Responsibilities and achievements:</strong></p>
        <ul class="experience-entry__list">
          <li>Developed new features for an employee absence tracking system.</li>
          <li>Maintained and improved the «Total Dictation» project.</li>
          <li>Configured Zabbix and monitoring integrations with web applications.</li>
          <li>Communicated with customers to clarify requirements, approve changes, and verify results.</li>
          <li>Improved business logic and supported legacy projects.</li>
        </ul>
      </article>

      <hr class="experience-divider" />

      <article class="experience-entry">
        <header class="experience-entry__header">
          <h3>Software Engineer</h3>
          <p class="experience-entry__meta">
            <span>Programmny Produkt — IT solutions development</span>
            <a href="https://ppr.ru" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow">ppr.ru</a>
          </p>
          <p class="experience-entry__period">July 2020 — June 2023</p>
        </header>
        <p>Developed and maintained web applications for major Moscow IT projects, including KOS portals, Mayor’s Grants, Immortal Regiment, Public Chamber, and others. Worked in a team of 15 specialists, including backend and frontend developers, analysts, and managers.</p>
        <div class="experience-entry__technologies">
          <p class="experience-entry__label">Technologies:</p>
          <ul class="technology-list">
            <li>PHP 7/8</li>
            <li>Symfony</li>
            <li>WordPress</li>
            <li>MariaDB</li>
            <li>PostgreSQL</li>
            <li>JavaScript</li>
            <li>Sphinx</li>
            <li>GitLab</li>
            <li>Ubuntu</li>
            <li>PhpStorm</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <p><strong>Responsibilities and achievements:</strong></p>
        <ul class="experience-entry__list">
          <li>Integrated Symfony and WordPress projects with external APIs, including Dadata.</li>
          <li>Developed a Symfony bundle for sitemap generation with flexible configuration.</li>
          <li>Created an intermediate layer between Sphinx and the application for advanced search.</li>
          <li>Developed and refactored business logic according to customer requirements.</li>
